The **Indobase Assistant** is an AI-powered tool engineered to augment Indobase-related tasks with technical precision. It operates on a foundation of training data sourced from the Indobase documentation website, enabling it to furnish insights into Indobase's features, APIs, and documentation. Additionally, it offers functionality for code snippet generation, sample project creation, and problem troubleshooting.

